high_descs: Turn right, walk to the middle of the couch, and turn around to face the coffee table.
Pick up the remote to the right of the box.
Turn around and face the red couch.
Put the remote down on the couch to the left of the credit card.
Turn around to face the coffee table.
Pick up the remote to the left of the box.
Turn around to face the couch again.
Put the remote down on the couch to the right of the credit card.
anns.task_desc: To move two remotes to the couch.

high_descs: Turn to your right and take eight steps, turn left taking four steps, then turn left to face the coffee table.
Pick up the remote control to the right of the cardboard box.
Turn around to face the red couch.
Lay the remote control horizontally on the couch, on the left cushion at the top of the light shadow to the left of the credit card with the top of the remote, facing to the right.
Turn right and walk two steps, take another right and stop, facing the coffee table.
Pick up the remote control from the table to the left of the cardboard box.
Turn right and take one step, turn right and face the red couch.
Place the remote control horizontally on the couch, above the light shadow to the right of the credit card with the top of the remote facing to the right.
anns.task_desc: Put two remote controls on the red couch.

high_descs: Go to the center table
Pick up the remote on the right
Go to the red sofa
Put the remote down on the sofa
Go to the center table
Pick up the remote on the left
Go to the red sofa
Put the remote down on the sofa
anns.task_desc: Move two remotes to a sofa
